---
title: North Indian Spiced Paneer Biryani with Roasted Cashews & Yoghurt
description: Forget what you think you know about biryani - this veggie version, using paneer instead of lamb, just goes to show that rules are made to be broken! It's sweet, spicy, satisfying and just the thing to warm you up on a chilly night.
